HEADWORD: Fightwite
<hw>Fight"wite`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Fight</ets>
+ <ets>wite</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(O.Eng. Law)</fld> <def>A mulct or fine
